  <data name="Winget_Description" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Software to annotate screenshot for Windows and Linux.

Features:
- **Arrows** - Draw attention to specific areas with customizable arrows
- **Callouts** - Add speech bubble annotations with editable text
- **Notes** - Create text boxes for extra information
- **Border selection** - Highlight areas with bordered rectangles
- **Blur** - Hide sensitive information with blur
- **Selection tool** - Select parts of image to copy (Ctrl+C) or delete (Delete key)
- **Cut vertical and horizontal slices** - Cut vertical or horizontal areas of image
- **Highlighter** - Highlight areas of interest
- **Project management** - Automatic project saving and preview thumbnails
- **Cross-platform** - E dey work for Windows and Linux</value>
  </data>
